<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="14" type="nomenclature">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="14">
<taxonomicName LSID="62D24127-8B51-586F-BDC2-EF1D0B900724" authority="Váňa, Hentschel, Joch. Müll. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityName="Váňa, Hentschel, Joch. Müll. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="Scapania" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="section" section="Hyperboreae" status="sect. nov.">
Scapania sect. Hyperboreae 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Váňa">Vana</normalizedToken>
, Hentschel, Joch. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Müll">Muell</normalizedToken>
. &amp; Heinrichs
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel pageId="1" pageNumber="14">sect. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="14" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Diagnosis.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="14">
Species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sect. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Hyperboreae</emphasis>
resemble members of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sect. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Curtae</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken originalValue="Müll">Muell</normalizedToken>
. Frib.) H. Buch but differ by the presence of brownish to reddish gemmae, and a usually larger size.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="14" type="type">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Type.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="14">
<taxonomicName class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="hyperborea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania hyperborea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Jørg">Jorg</normalizedToken>
., 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Förh">Foerh</normalizedToken>
. Vidensk.-Selsk. Kristiania 1894(8): 56. 1894.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="1" pageNumber="14" type="note">
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Note.</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="1" pageNumber="14">
The presence of the type species of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sect. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Irriguae</emphasis>
(
<normalizedToken originalValue="Müll">Muell</normalizedToken>
. Frib.) H. Buch, 
<taxonomicName class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="irrigua">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania irrigua</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nees) Nees, in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sect. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Curtae</emphasis>
necessitates the introduction of a new section for the remaining elements of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sect. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Irriguae</emphasis>
. Molecular data so far supported the presence of 
<taxonomicName class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="paludicola">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania paludicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
Loeske &amp; 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Müll">Muell</normalizedToken>
. Frib. and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="H. Buch" authorityYear="1928" baseAuthorityName="Arnell" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="tundrae">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania tundrae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Arnell) H. Buch in 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">S.</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
subg. 
<taxonomicName authorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" authorityYear="2012" baseAuthorityName="sect. Simmonsia (R. M. Schust.) Vana, Hentschel, Joch. Muell. &amp; Heinrichs" baseAuthorityYear="2012" class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
sect. 
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Hyperboreae</emphasis>
, as well as 
<taxonomicName class="Hepaticae" family="Scapaniaceae" genus="Scapania" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Plantae" lsidName="" order="Jungermanniales" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" phylum="Bryophyta" rank="species" species="hyperborea">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="14">Scapania hyperborea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(
<bibRefCitation author="Vilnet, AA" journalOrPublisher="Arctoa" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" pagination="31 - 50" refId="B5" refString="Vilnet, AA, Konstantinova, NA, Troitsky, AV, 2010. Molecular insight on phylogeny and systematics of Lophoziaceae, Scapaniaceae, Gymnomitriaceae and Jungermanniaceae. Arctoa 19: 31 - 50" title="Molecular insight on phylogeny and systematics of Lophoziaceae, Scapaniaceae, Gymnomitriaceae and Jungermanniaceae." volume="19" year="2010">Vilnet et al. 2010</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Heinrichs, J" journalOrPublisher="Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution" pageId="1" pageNumber="14" pagination="973 - 985" publicationUrl="10.1016/j.ympev.2011.11.029" refId="B2" refString="Heinrichs, J, Bombosch, A, Feldberg, K, Kreier, HP, Hentschel, J, Eckstein, J, Long, D, Zhu, RL, Schaefer-Verwimp, A, Schmidt, AR, Shaw, B, Shaw, AJ, Vana, J, 2012. A phylogeny of the northern temperate leafy liverwort genus Scapania (Scapaniaceae, Jungermanniales). Molecular Phylogenetics and Evolution 62: 973 - 985, 10.1016/j.ympev.2011.11.029" title="A phylogeny of the northern temperate leafy liverwort genus Scapania (Scapaniaceae, Jungermanniales)." url="10.1016/j.ympev.2011.11.029" volume="62" year="2012">Heinrichs et al. 2012</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
